-- Corvex Group Offers to Buy CommonWealth REIT for $24.50 a Share
-- B y   B r i a n   L o u i s
-- 2013-03-28T17:11:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-28/corvex-group-offers-to-buy-commonwealth-reit-for-24-50-a-share.html
Corvex Management LP and Related
Cos offered to buy  CommonWealth REIT (CWH)  for $24.50 a share and said
they will pursue removing the company’s board if a takeover bid
isn’t accepted.  The proposal represents a reduction from the investor
group’s February bid of $27 a share following a CommonWealth
equity offering, Corvex and Related said today in a statement.
They own about 9 percent of the real estate investment trust.  To contact the reporter on this story:
